Description
-----------

This CVar defines the aspect ratio used when using a custom video
resolution.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    r_aspectRatio [int]

Parameters
----------

-   [Int]
    -   0 - 4/3.
    -   1 - 16/9.
    -   2 - 16/10.

